{"tid":2506477,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「全裸」上生物課　美女師「器官無碼全露」教學獲激賞","createTime":"2021-04-27T10:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T10:46:11.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb05a527a4076a1e5aed627b9bbcdd6be4d7ffc","tid":2506477,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3128998-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3128998-PH.jpg&h=9e32e900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3129001-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3129001-PH.jpg&h=624c068a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3128999-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3128999-PH.jpg&h=5fbc36c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如何增加孩子的學習興趣，一次就記住！是考驗許多老師教學的本領！西班牙有一位教生<br />\n物課的美女老師叫維羅妮卡，教學方式非常創新，上課竟然「全裸」，而且孩子們都喜歡<br />\n上她的課，不但讓孩子一次就記住，還印象深刻，連家長都相當激賞！<br />\n <br />\n維羅妮卡老師，在上生物課時，為了能夠讓孩子理解得更透徹，竟穿了帶有人體器官的衣<br />\n服去上課，只看得到器官宛如「全裸」，讓孩子既好奇又有點害怕。身上每個器官「一目<br />\n了然」，一剛開始看，有學生表示「的確有些突兀」。也有孩子發現，「原來腸子就是長<br />\n這樣子」，心臟的模樣清清楚楚。<br />\n <br />\n老師強調，尤其生理器官，孩子了解的也不盡全面。大多數家長以為等孩子長大就懂了，<br />\n也就不怎麼重視，「對孩子直接簡單明瞭的說讓孩子記得更深刻，也讓孩子有自我保護的<br />\n意識。」老師的苦心，還自製了一套人體器官圖，讓上課多點趣味與娛樂，也受到不少家<br />\n長激賞！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=930993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D930993&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oA7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=1c7d359d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D930993&h=81b3b376\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=930993</a>"},{"pid":"957ed27f2f47fc